{"tid":2089216,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方：譴責網媒不用廣角鏡  譴責記者粗言穢語","createTime":"2020-07-01T14:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T15:05:15.000Z","uid":7542,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9b50dab05b12596ed0120ec7a1a2f4a133ffed4b","tid":2089216,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T14:15:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>警察就嚟要入廚房教埋廚師煮嘢食</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傍晚有示威者將大量印有不同警員個人資料的紙張，散落於銅鑼灣時代廣場二樓大堂的地上。警方在社交專頁表示，禁止對警員、特務警員及其家屬起底和滋擾的臨時禁制令仍然生效，警方保留對違反禁制令者追究的權利。警方表示，有網媒在網上直播期間，以特寫鏡頭拍攝這些印有不同警員個人資料的紙張，<strong>亦於直播期間粗言穢語</strong>。警方認為有關舉動等同加添對被起底警員的傷害，極不恰當。<strong>警方認為以廣角鏡頭拍攝同樣可達致報道的效果，對有關舉動表示遺憾</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535264-20200701.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535264-20200701.htm&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9bHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=e11b48f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535264-20200701.htm&h=6bef7211\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535264-20200701.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果你唔知今日發生嘅事，同當年納粹發生嘅事有幾相似。嘥你<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>90秒</ins></strong></span>睇一條片：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xbFFY9CPduw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxbFFY9CPduw&d=Ia4lQUE8yf8cF0bf%2B23B9bHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=3aaab910\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xbFFY9CPduw</a>"},{"pid":"15c9b489db2d249ce2e65256851ecce1d03e4a40","tid":2089216,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"